<item>
            <title>[SPR-1000] Only Maven.xml (not Build.xml) includes JNDI classes into spring-jdbc.jar</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-1000</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the &quot;spring-framework-1.2.1-with-dependencies&quot; distribution, the spring.jar in the &quot;dist&quot; directory includes the org.springframework.jndi.* classes.  However, the spring-jdbc.jar does not include the jndi classes.  No other &quot;modular&quot; jar appears to contain the JNDI classes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The maven.xml file specifies that the org.springframework.jndi.* classes should be included in the spring-jdbc.jar.  But, the build.xml file does not include the jndi classes in the spring-jdbc.jar.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I would think that there probably shouldn&apos;t be a discrepancy in the jars that the build.xml and the maven.xml produce.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If there is supposed to be a discrepancy in the jdbc jar that each of the build processes produce, can the org.springframework.jndi.* classes be included in one of the &quot;modular&quot; jars rather than only in the master 1.6mb distribution spring.jar?&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;MAVEN.XML ---&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;jar jarfile=&quot;$&lt;/p&gt;
{maven.build.dir}
&lt;p&gt;/spring-jdbc-$&lt;/p&gt;
{pom.currentVersion}
&lt;p&gt;.jar&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;fileset dir=&quot;$&lt;/p&gt;
{maven.build.dest}
&lt;p&gt;&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;include name=&quot;org/springframework/aop/**&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;include name=&quot;org/springframework/beans/**&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;include name=&quot;org/springframework/core/**&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;include name=&quot;org/springframework/dao/**&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;include name=&quot;org/springframework/jdbc/**&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   &amp;lt;include name=&quot;org/springframework/jndi/**&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   &amp;lt;include name=&quot;org/springframework/orm/**&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;include name=&quot;org/springframework/transaction/**&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;include name=&quot;org/springframework/util/*&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/fileset&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/jar&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;BUILD.XML ---&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;jar jarfile=&quot;$&lt;/p&gt;
{dist.dir}
&lt;p&gt;/spring-jdbc.jar&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;fileset dir=&quot;$&lt;/p&gt;
{target.classes.dir}
&lt;p&gt;&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   &amp;lt;include name=&quot;org/springframework/jdbc/**&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;/fileset&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;manifest&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;attribute name=&quot;Implementation-Title&quot; value=&quot;$&lt;/p&gt;
{spring-title}
&lt;p&gt;&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;attribute name=&quot;Implementation-Version&quot; value=&quot;$&lt;/p&gt;
{spring-version}&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;attribute name=&quot;Spring-Version&quot; value=&quot;${spring-version}
&lt;p&gt;&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/manifest&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/jar&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
